1 - MAKE SURE LUAJIT IS INSTALLED

2 - INSTALL LUAJIT BINDINGS FOR OCAML
	git clone -b luajit https://github.com/pdonadeo/ocaml-lua.git
	cd ocaml-lua/
  	./configure --enable-luajit --enable-memory-test --enable-debug --enable-stub-debug --enable-examples && make
	make install

3 - INSTALL DEDUKTI
	cd dkparse
	make
	make install
	
TROUBLESHOUTING
	Make sure the lua bindings are installed in the correct directory [/usr/lib/ocaml ?]
	Make sure the file dedukti.lua is installed in the correct directory [/usr/share/luajit* ?]
